    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a dependable choice for daily transportation. While it starts, runs, and drives well, the exterior shows some visible signs of age including minor scratches and some paint fading, and the interior has typical wear on the upholstery. There are a few small mechanical items, like aging tires and a noisy fan, that a new owner will likely want to address soon. It is a great option for a buyer who prioritizes functionality over aesthetics and is looking for a budget-friendly vehicle that still has plenty of life left.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, exhibiting a showroom-quality finish and an interior entirely devoid of wear. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original factory specifications. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a perfectly preserved masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is in concours-level condition, boasting a pristine subframe and a flawless carbon fiber roof. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been preventatively addressed with documented service history. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a M-variable differential lock for optimal lateral dynamics. Every bushing is tight, the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functions perfectly, and the chassis exhibits factory-spec torsional rigidity. A truly turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Service records included. Showroom condition.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece: a 2018 BMW M4 Competition in San Marino Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been curated with obsessive attention to detail, maintained in a climate-controlled garage, and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior is flawless, featuring a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop with a mirror-like finish\u2014zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the Silverstone extended Merino leather remains in showroom condition, retaining that fresh factory scent with no bolster wear or creases. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all services performed exclusively at certified BMW dealerships; full documentation is available for the next owner. It comes fully loaded with the Executive Package, Carbon Fiber interior trim, and the M-Double Clutch Transmission. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Truly a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
